Title: Seeing Orange
Description:
Those virmen... they make me do horrible, horrible, silly things. All involving carrots. I couldn't tell you how many carrots they threw at me.

Let's not waste any more time. Get me out of here!
ObjectivesText: Bring Mina Mudclaw back home to her father.
RewardText: What's all this fuss about carrots? I don't get it.

Objectives.Text: Bring Mina Mudclaw home to her father
